name: Tokens of the past
description:
Click or tap on the game to activate it. 

If you’re on a desktop, use your arrow keys to navigate.

If you’re on mobile, swipe in the direction of the in-game arrows to navigate.

This game as been created for mildmojo as part of Bitsy Community Secret Santa 2020

The prompts were

ENOUGH
CUSP
TOKENS OF THE PAST

and that's what I came up with.

Made with Bitsy and Borksy
